{"tid":1848560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街喇！原來街市超市賣嘅雞蛋，好多嚟自湖北","createTime":"2020-01-28T13:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T14:47:15.000Z","uid":80270,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0a77ed335fcf31cd39bcdf3a325c245dc7629347","tid":1848560,"uid":80270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:52:53.000Z","msg":"當大家都為口罩煩惱緊緊嘅時候，原來香港每年由中國進口嘅雞蛋有60%係來自中國，而送嚟香港嘅蛋蛋，又有為數不少係來自湖北。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隨便Google 下都已經有唔少湖北蛋嘅資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/教煮/102818/8大雞蛋逐隻剝-蒸炒煎焗一蛋走江湖-大廚有心水推介\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%95%99%E7%85%AE%2F102818%2F8%E5%A4%A7%E9%9B%9E%E8%9B%8B%E9%80%90%E9%9A%BB%E5%89%9D-%E8%92%B8%E7%82%92%E7%85%8E%E7%84%97%E4%B8%80%E8%9B%8B%E8%B5%B0%E6%B1%9F%E6%B9%96-%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%9A%E6%9C%89%E5%BF%83%E6%B0%B4%E6%8E%A8%E4%BB%8B&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=adea9878\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/教煮/102818/8大雞蛋逐隻剝-蒸炒煎焗一蛋走江湖-大廚有心水推介</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/181989/多黃出奇蛋-市民買16隻湖北蛋-驚見孖卵-三卵佔15隻\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F181989%2F%E5%A4%9A%E9%BB%83%E5%87%BA%E5%A5%87%E8%9B%8B-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%B2%B716%E9%9A%BB%E6%B9%96%E5%8C%97%E8%9B%8B-%E9%A9%9A%E8%A6%8B%E5%AD%96%E5%8D%B5-%E4%B8%89%E5%8D%B5%E4%BD%9415%E9%9A%BB&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=0bf5cd44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/181989/多黃出奇蛋-市民買16隻湖北蛋-驚見孖卵-三卵佔15隻</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20180131/mobile/odn-20180131-0131_00296_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20180131%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20180131-0131_00296_001.html&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGS